For example
@code{(7)} is a compact way of writing @code{(7 . ())},
@code{(1 2)} is a compact way of writing @code{(1 . (2 . ()))},
@code{((a))} is a compact way of writing @code{((a . ()) . ())},
and @code{(10 a . #t)} is a compact way of writing the non-list
@code{(10 . (a . #t))}.

